\hypertarget{create-table-aircraft}{%
\subsection{CREATE TABLE: Aircraft}\label{create-table-aircraft}}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\KeywordTok{DROP} \KeywordTok{TABLE} \ControlFlowTok{IF} \KeywordTok{EXISTS}\NormalTok{ Aircraft;}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\KeywordTok{CREATE} \KeywordTok{TABLE}\NormalTok{ Aircraft(}
\NormalTok{  a\_id }\DataTypeTok{INTEGER} \KeywordTok{PRIMARY} \KeywordTok{KEY}\NormalTok{ AUTO\_INCREMENT,}
\NormalTok{  aircraft\_name }\DataTypeTok{VARCHAR}\NormalTok{(}\DecValTok{255}\NormalTok{) }\KeywordTok{UNIQUE} \KeywordTok{NOT} \KeywordTok{NULL}\NormalTok{,      }\CommentTok{{-}{-} }\AlertTok{TODO}\CommentTok{: We added unique here}
\NormalTok{  aircraft\_type ENUM(}\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}Airplane\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}UNKNOWN\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{) }\KeywordTok{NOT} \KeywordTok{NULL}\NormalTok{,}
\NormalTok{  number\_engines ENUM(}\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}1\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}2\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}3\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}4\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}5\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}6\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}7\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}8\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}UNKNOWN\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{) }\KeywordTok{NOT} \KeywordTok{NULL}\NormalTok{,}
\NormalTok{  large\_aircraft ENUM(}\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}Yes\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}No\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}UNKNOWN\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{) }\KeywordTok{NOT} \KeywordTok{NULL}
\NormalTok{  );}
  
\CommentTok{{-}{-} assumption: we are assuming that each model for the airplane has only one engine configuration so we are correcting for it before uploading the table using a mode calculation. }
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\# If value was uploaded as UNKNOWN, set the date to 1/1/1776. Otherwise, parse the date as is.}
\ControlFlowTok{for}\NormalTok{ (row }\ControlFlowTok{in} \DecValTok{1}\SpecialCharTok{:}\FunctionTok{nrow}\NormalTok{(birdStrike\_df))\{}
\NormalTok{  date\_time\_string }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{unlist}\NormalTok{(birdStrike\_df[row, }\StringTok{"FlightDate"}\NormalTok{])}
  \ControlFlowTok{if}\NormalTok{ (date\_time\_string }\SpecialCharTok{==} \StringTok{"UNKNOWN"}\NormalTok{)\{}
\NormalTok{    date\_time\_parsed }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{as.Date}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{as.character}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{as.POSIXct}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"1/1/1776 0:00"}\NormalTok{, }\AttributeTok{format=}\StringTok{"\%m/\%d/\%Y \%H:\%M"}\NormalTok{)))}
\NormalTok{  \} }\ControlFlowTok{else}\NormalTok{ \{}
\NormalTok{    date\_time\_parsed }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{as.Date}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{as.character}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{as.POSIXct}\NormalTok{(date\_time\_string, }\AttributeTok{format=}\StringTok{"\%m/\%d/\%Y \%H:\%M"}\NormalTok{)))}
\NormalTok{  \}}
\NormalTok{  birdStrike\_df[row, }\StringTok{"flight\_date"}\NormalTok{] }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\NormalTok{ date\_time\_parsed}
\NormalTok{\}}

\CommentTok{\# Assumption:}
\CommentTok{\#  {-} For unknown dates, it is set to 1776}

\CommentTok{\# Query State Data from Database}

\NormalTok{stateDataTemp }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{sqldf}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}SELECT DISTINCT "Airport..Name" AS airport\_name}

\StringTok{                       JOIN stateDataFromDatabase}

\StringTok{                     , state\_id}
\StringTok{                     FROM stateDataTemp}

\CommentTok{\# Query df to generate list of aircraft and numengines}
\NormalTok{AircraftNumEnginesOnlyDF }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{sqldf}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}SELECT "Aircraft..Make.Model" AS Aircraft,}

\StringTok{                                  , most\_common\_engine AS number\_engines }

\CommentTok{\# Query dataframe to pull in large\_aircraft attribute for each aircraft}
\NormalTok{AircraftTableLargeAircraft }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{sqldf}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}SELECT DISTINCT "Aircraft..Make.Model" AS name,}
\StringTok{                                    "Aircraft..Type" AS aircraft\_type,}
\StringTok{                                    "Is.Aircraft.Large." AS large\_aircraft}
\StringTok{                                    FROM birdStrike\_df}
\StringTok{                                    GROUP BY name\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{)}

\CommentTok{\# Union df that has engine setup with df that has aircraft\_type and large\_aircraft}
\NormalTok{AircraftTable }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{sqldf}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}SELECT rest.name AS aircraft\_name}
\StringTok{                       , rest.aircraft\_type}
\StringTok{                       , engines.number\_engines}
\StringTok{                       , rest.large\_aircraft}
\StringTok{                       FROM AircraftTableLargeAircraft AS rest}
\StringTok{                       JOIN AircraftTableEnginesOnly AS engines}
\StringTok{                       ON rest.name = engines.name}
\StringTok{                       ORDER BY rest.name\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{)}

\hypertarget{prepare-data-flight}{%
\subsection{PREPARE DATA: Flight}\label{prepare-data-flight}}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\# Query information from database, needed to join everything together}
\NormalTok{AircraftFromAWS }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{dbGetQuery}\NormalTok{(mydb, }\StringTok{"SELECT * FROM Aircraft;"}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{AirportFromAWS }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{dbGetQuery}\NormalTok{(mydb, }\StringTok{"SELECT * FROM Airport;"}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{AirlineOperatorFromAWS }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{dbGetQuery}\NormalTok{(mydb, }\StringTok{"SELECT * FROM AirlineOperator;"}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{StateFromAWS }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{dbGetQuery}\NormalTok{(mydb, }\StringTok{"SELECT * FROM State;"}\NormalTok{)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\# Start by joining in Aircraft data}
\NormalTok{FlightTableWithAircraft }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{sqldf}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}SELECT "UniqueKey" as f\_id, "Record.ID" AS record\_id, flight\_date}
\StringTok{                                  , aircraft.a\_id AS aircraft\_id, aircraft.aircraft\_name AS aircraft\_name}
\StringTok{                                  , "Airport..Name" AS airport\_name}
\StringTok{                                  , "Origin.State" AS origin\_state}
\StringTok{                                  , "Aircraft..Airline.Operator"}
\StringTok{                                  FROM birdStrike\_df}
\StringTok{                                  JOIN AircraftFromAWS AS aircraft}
\StringTok{                                  ON "Aircraft..Make.Model" = aircraft.aircraft\_name\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{)}

\CommentTok{\# Then add in state}
\NormalTok{FlightTableWithAircraft\_State }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{sqldf}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{\textquotesingle{}SELECT *}
\StringTok{                                        FROM FlightTableWithAircraft}
\StringTok{                                        JOIN StateFromAWS}

\hypertarget{pts-3-hrs-using-the-above-data-build-a-column-chart-that-visualizes-the-number-of-bird-strikes-incidents-per-year-from-2008-to-2011-during-take-offclimbing-and-during-descentapproachlanding.-adorn-the-graph-with-appropriate-axis-labels.}{%
\subsubsection{7. (10 pts / 3 hrs) Using the above data, build a column
chart that visualizes the number of bird strikes incidents per year from
2008 to 2011 during take-off/climbing and during
descent/approach/landing. Adorn the graph with appropriate axis
labels.}\label{pts-3-hrs-using-the-above-data-build-a-column-chart-that-visualizes-the-number-of-bird-strikes-incidents-per-year-from-2008-to-2011-during-take-offclimbing-and-during-descentapproachlanding.-adorn-the-graph-with-appropriate-axis-labels.}}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\# pulling the data together into a data frame}
\NormalTok{BirdstrikesPerYear }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{dbGetQuery}\NormalTok{(mydb, }
                            \StringTok{\textquotesingle{}SELECT * FROM }
\StringTok{                            (SELECT COUNT(BirdStrike.birdstrike\_id) as incidents}
\StringTok{                            , CASE }
\StringTok{                              WHEN phase\_of\_flight = "Take{-}off run" THEN "Ascent"}
\StringTok{                              WHEN phase\_of\_flight = "Climb" THEN "Ascent"}
\StringTok{                              WHEN phase\_of\_flight = "Descent" THEN "Descent"}
\StringTok{                              WHEN phase\_of\_flight = "Approach" THEN "Descent"}
\StringTok{                              WHEN phase\_of\_flight = "Landing Roll" THEN "Descent"}
\StringTok{                            END as phase}
\StringTok{                            , YEAR(Flight.flight\_date) as Year}
\StringTok{                            FROM BirdStrike}
\StringTok{                            JOIN Flight}
\StringTok{                            ON BirdStrike.flight\_id = Flight.f\_id}
\StringTok{                            WHERE YEAR(Flight.flight\_date) \textgreater{}= 2008}
\StringTok{                            and YEAR(Flight.flight\_date) \textless{}= 2011}
\StringTok{                            GROUP BY YEAR(Flight.flight\_date), phase}
\StringTok{                            ORDER BY Year) t}
\StringTok{                            WHERE phase = ("Ascent" OR "Descent")\textquotesingle{}}\NormalTok{)}

\CommentTok{\#initializing the data}
\NormalTok{condition }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\NormalTok{ BirdstrikesPerYear}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{phase}
\NormalTok{years }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\NormalTok{ BirdstrikesPerYear}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Year}
\NormalTok{incidents }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\NormalTok{ BirdstrikesPerYear}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{incidents}

\CommentTok{\# adorning the bar chart}
\NormalTok{barChart }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{ggplot}\NormalTok{(}\AttributeTok{data =}\NormalTok{ BirdstrikesPerYear, }\FunctionTok{aes}\NormalTok{(}\AttributeTok{fille =}\NormalTok{ condition, }\AttributeTok{x =}\NormalTok{ years, }\AttributeTok{y =}\NormalTok{ incidents, }\AttributeTok{fill =}\NormalTok{ condition)) }\SpecialCharTok{+} \FunctionTok{geom\_bar}\NormalTok{(}\AttributeTok{stat =} \StringTok{"identity"}\NormalTok{, }\AttributeTok{position =} \StringTok{"dodge"}\NormalTok{) }\SpecialCharTok{+} \FunctionTok{ggtitle}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"Bird Strikes Per Year By Phase of Flight"}\NormalTok{)}
\FunctionTok{print}\NormalTok{(barChart)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

(note that if you used SQLite, then you cannot complete this step) that

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\KeywordTok{DROP} \KeywordTok{PROCEDURE} \ControlFlowTok{IF} \KeywordTok{EXISTS}\NormalTok{ Remove\_BirdStrike;}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\KeywordTok{CREATE} \KeywordTok{PROCEDURE}\NormalTok{ Remove\_BirdStrike (}
  \KeywordTok{IN}\NormalTok{ birdstrike\_id\_to\_delete }\DataTypeTok{INTEGER}\NormalTok{)}
\ControlFlowTok{BEGIN}
  \CommentTok{{-}{-} Save the note\_id, which will be needed for deletion later}
  \KeywordTok{DECLARE}\NormalTok{ delete\_note\_id }\DataTypeTok{INTEGER}\NormalTok{;}
  \KeywordTok{SET}\NormalTok{ delete\_note\_id }\OperatorTok{=}\NormalTok{ (}\KeywordTok{SELECT}\NormalTok{ BirdStrike.note\_id}
                        \KeywordTok{FROM}\NormalTok{ BirdStrike}
                        \KeywordTok{WHERE}\NormalTok{ BirdStrike.birdstrike\_id }\OperatorTok{=}\NormalTok{ birdstrike\_id\_to\_delete);}
  
  \CommentTok{{-}{-} Remove the associated precipitation records}
  \KeywordTok{DELETE} \KeywordTok{FROM}\NormalTok{ Precipitation }\KeywordTok{WHERE}\NormalTok{ Precipitation.birdstrike\_id }\OperatorTok{=}\NormalTok{ birdstrike\_id\_to\_delete;}
  
  \CommentTok{{-}{-} Remove the birdstrike record}
  \KeywordTok{DELETE} \KeywordTok{FROM}\NormalTok{ BirdStrike }\KeywordTok{WHERE}\NormalTok{ BirdStrike.birdstrike\_id }\OperatorTok{=}\NormalTok{ birdstrike\_id\_to\_delete;}
  
  \CommentTok{{-}{-} Remove the note record}
  \KeywordTok{DELETE} \KeywordTok{FROM}\NormalTok{ Note }\KeywordTok{WHERE}\NormalTok{ Note.n\_id }\OperatorTok{=}\NormalTok{ delete\_note\_id;}
  
    \CommentTok{{-}{-} Remove the corresponding flight}
  \KeywordTok{DELETE} \KeywordTok{FROM}\NormalTok{ Flight }\KeywordTok{WHERE}\NormalTok{ Flight.f\_id }\OperatorTok{=}\NormalTok{ (}\KeywordTok{SELECT}\NormalTok{ BirdStrike.flight\_id}
                                          \KeywordTok{FROM}\NormalTok{ BirdStrike}
                                          \KeywordTok{WHERE}\NormalTok{ BirdStrike.birdstrike\_id }\OperatorTok{=}\NormalTok{ birdstrike\_id\_to\_delete);}

\ControlFlowTok{END}\NormalTok{;}
\end{Highlighting}
